1
00:01:32,090 --> 00:01:34,890
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:37,910
[Episode 9]

3
00:01:38,979 --> 00:01:40,710
What Flower Festival Banquet?

4
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:43,970
I think they're just bored
and want to waste money.

5
00:01:44,030 --> 00:01:46,229
Common people can barely afford to eat,

6
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,520
yet they still have time
for such frivolities.

7
00:01:53,250 --> 00:01:54,610
This isn't the way back to the palace.

8
00:01:54,610 --> 00:01:56,830
I didn't dare call out to you
since you were walking this way

9
00:01:56,830 --> 00:01:57,960
with your head down.

10
00:01:57,970 --> 00:01:58,570
No wonder.

11
00:01:58,890 --> 00:02:00,090
-Let's—
-Consort Yu.

12
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:04,770
The palace is so big,

13
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,570
yet somehow I run into him everywhere.

14
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:08,370
Such bad luck.

15
00:02:08,410 --> 00:02:09,270
Your Highness.

16
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,090
Consort Yu.

17
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:16,340
May I have a word with you?

18
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,550
Wait for me over there.

19
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:20,660
Yes.

20
00:02:25,570 --> 00:02:26,430
Your Highness,

21
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,650
what brings you here?

22
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,770
When I was young
and hadn't left the palace,

23
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:34,210
if the servants beat me,

24
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,410
I'd hide here

25
00:02:38,990 --> 00:02:40,650
and only return late at night.

26
00:02:41,550 --> 00:02:42,890
So now that I have time,

27
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:45,590
I wanted to come back and take a look.

28
00:02:45,730 --> 00:02:46,530
Here it comes.

29
00:02:46,990 --> 00:02:48,780
The villain's monologue.

30
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:51,730
Wanyin.

31
00:02:53,510 --> 00:02:54,510
Why do I feel that

32
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,790
we've grown distant?

33
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,320
It's not that.

34
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,580
It's just that this place

35
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,270
has too many prying eyes.

36
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:06,150
My secret guards are watching the area.

37
00:03:06,610 --> 00:03:07,540
No one will come.

38
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:18,700
Regarding what I said last time,

39
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:20,210
have you thought about it?

40
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,540
Can Your Highness foresee

41
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:24,680
my decision too?

42
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:26,780
What do you think?

43
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,400
Dodging the question.

44
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:32,290
Good thing I'm prepared.

45
00:03:35,270 --> 00:03:36,760
I panicked that day,

46
00:03:36,890 --> 00:03:37,930
and my words

47
00:03:38,770 --> 00:03:40,630
may have offended Your Highness.

48
00:03:41,530 --> 00:03:43,060
I embroidered this myself.

49
00:03:48,530 --> 00:03:49,320
Swallows

50
00:03:51,170 --> 00:03:52,170
flying together.

51
00:03:53,110 --> 00:03:55,310
It's "The Return of the Condor Heroes."

52
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:57,880
You must've put some thought into this.

53
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,740
As long as Your Highness likes it.

54
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:01,940
Your Highness predicts things like a god,

55
00:04:01,940 --> 00:04:03,580
always making a move first.

56
00:04:05,060 --> 00:04:06,790
Could it be that you are also...

57
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:07,830
Also what?

58
00:04:08,270 --> 00:04:09,620
One with foresight?

59
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:15,450
Yes.

60
00:04:16,610 --> 00:04:17,529
I gained it

61
00:04:19,350 --> 00:04:19,870
quite recently.

62
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:20,769
In your dreams,

63
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,930
do you often see

64
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:24,370
strange sights

65
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:26,930
but don't know what they mean?

66
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,120
They look...

67
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:32,500
quite blurry.

68
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,570
Dream interpretation is difficult.

69
00:04:34,570 --> 00:04:36,370
It's hard to explain it clearly.

70
00:04:36,970 --> 00:04:38,970
It is said those of the highest level

71
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,480
can see all beings in the Six Realms.

72
00:04:41,730 --> 00:04:43,260
Just by closing their eyes,

73
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,450
they can reveal heaven's secrets.

74
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,820
But everyone is different,

75
00:04:48,409 --> 00:04:49,800
so what they see

76
00:04:50,210 --> 00:04:51,180
varies.

77
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:52,510
Makes sense.

78
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:55,250
Since Your Highness is a prince,

79
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:57,340
can you see more?

80
00:04:57,890 --> 00:04:59,550
Things further in the future?

81
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:01,960
A few days ago, I foresaw in a dream

82
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:03,910
that an expert appeared
beside His Majesty.

83
00:05:03,910 --> 00:05:05,430
He took you out of the palace in disguise

84
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,400
to a lake

85
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:08,370
to speak with some commoners.

86
00:05:08,370 --> 00:05:10,570
I was merely worried about your safety,

87
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:13,870
so I sent men to follow you secretly.

88
00:05:14,740 --> 00:05:17,340
But unexpectedly,
this expert acted without any warning

89
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:19,340
and killed many of my secret guards.

90
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,450
With such a dangerous person by your side,

91
00:05:22,490 --> 00:05:24,150
how can I be at ease?

92
00:05:25,460 --> 00:05:26,760
He beat around the bush

93
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:28,520
just to get things out of me.

94
00:05:28,990 --> 00:05:30,450
I'd never seen this person

95
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:31,910
in the palace either.

96
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:34,430
I was truly terrified that day.

97
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:36,909
What about after returning to the palace?

98
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:38,380
Have you seen him?

99
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:40,780
No, I haven't.

100
00:05:41,930 --> 00:05:42,700
Is that so?

101
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:45,980
Your Highness,

102
00:05:46,890 --> 00:05:48,090
do you not believe me?

103
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,080
Of course not.

104
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,170
I wonder if you could use your foresight

105
00:05:56,170 --> 00:05:57,030
to divine for me

106
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:59,030
where this person

107
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,480
is right now.

108
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:04,010
Doesn't Your Highness know

109
00:06:04,010 --> 00:06:05,320
that the scenes in the dreams

110
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,260
are bizarre

111
00:06:06,690 --> 00:06:08,620
and bestowed by the will of Heaven.

112
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,440
It is not something we can dream

113
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,770
just because we want to.

114
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,780
Perhaps, just for my sake,

115
00:06:19,590 --> 00:06:20,360
give it a try,

116
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:21,880
will you?

117
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:35,909
Insidious.

118
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:37,100
Cunning.

119
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:39,070
-My Lady, wait for me!
-Thick-skinned too!

120
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,110
My Lady!

121
00:06:40,060 --> 00:06:41,950
[Zhaoyang Hall]

122
00:06:42,460 --> 00:06:43,460
I'm so pissed off.

123
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:50,330
It's exhausting every time I talk to him.

124
00:06:50,710 --> 00:06:52,900
What does Xie Yong'er see in him anyway?

125
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:55,300
He flirts everywhere and plays both sides.

126
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:59,700
Quite fitting of his name Duan
which means to balance both sides.

127
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:03,490
Your Highness,

128
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,830
Dan has something very important

129
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:06,510
for you.

130
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:08,340
What?

131
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:15,080
Dan asked me to watch you
practice calligraphy.

132
00:07:17,210 --> 00:07:18,060
Calligraphy?

133
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,140
I did want to practice brush writing,

134
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:23,710
but I have other things
to think about now.

135
00:07:23,890 --> 00:07:24,690
I have no time.

136
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,660
You can always make time.

137
00:07:25,910 --> 00:07:27,480
[Yong]

138
00:07:29,890 --> 00:07:30,780
Besides,

139
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:32,000
Dan said Your Highness

140
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,030
only needs to practice
the character "Yong" well,

141
00:07:34,030 --> 00:07:35,960
and you'll master all characters.

142
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:37,890
He wrote this for you personally.

143
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:40,700
[Yong]

144
00:07:38,409 --> 00:07:40,340
Don't let his kindness go to waste.

145
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:45,020
It looks pretty decent.

146
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:47,070
When did he practice this behind my back?

147
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,659
Just practice, Your Highness.

148
00:07:48,659 --> 00:07:49,990
I'll stay here with you.

149
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:51,150
I won't go anywhere.

150
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:00,780
Yong.

151
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:06,510
Yong.

152
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:08,220
Yong.

153
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:10,330
The "Yong" in Xie Yong'er.

154
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:14,420
Yong.

155
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:15,660
Crap.

156
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,930
I fell for Prince Duan's trap.

157
00:08:17,980 --> 00:08:19,220
All that nonsense I spouted—

158
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:21,020
he definitely didn't buy it all.

159
00:08:21,780 --> 00:08:23,240
With his cautious nature,

160
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:26,070
he might go check with
Xie Yong'er right away.

161
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:29,270
If Xie Yong'er doesn't say
she gained the foresight,

162
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:30,990
and our stories don't match,

163
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:32,169
then I'm doomed.

164
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:33,630
Mr. Bei.

165
00:08:34,570 --> 00:08:35,350
Tell me,

166
00:08:35,770 --> 00:08:37,830
how can you make someone keep a secret

167
00:08:37,890 --> 00:08:39,150
and not tell anyone else?

168
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:41,150
How is your relationship with them?

169
00:08:41,289 --> 00:08:42,140
Not good.

170
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:43,610
Whatever I say,

171
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:45,420
she won't believe a single word.

172
00:08:45,420 --> 00:08:46,080
Lock her up.

173
00:08:46,180 --> 00:08:47,010
That won't work.

174
00:08:47,010 --> 00:08:48,180
I can't lock her up forever.

175
00:08:48,180 --> 00:08:49,180
Then silence her.

176
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:50,160
That's even worse.

177
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,100
She has to stay alive.

178
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:52,100
Then I don't know.

179
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:53,910
Nothing works.

180
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:55,220
What should I do?

181
00:09:00,110 --> 00:09:00,970
Your Highness.

182
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:02,570
You...

183
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:07,790
[Yong]

184
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,120
Oh shoot.

185
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:08,260
What the hell did I write?

186
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:09,780
Your handwriting, Your Highness,

187
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:11,350
is like wandering dragons
and painted phoenixes.

188
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:12,880
If you take it to the market,

189
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,880
it could ward off evil spirits.

190
00:09:17,050 --> 00:09:19,050
Thanks for the compliment, Mr. Bei.

191
00:09:22,660 --> 00:09:24,060
Ward off evil spirits...

192
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:25,200
I got it!

193
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:28,590
Prince Duan is definitely a 2D character.

194
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:31,590
He suspects you, me,
and Xie Yong'er are the same kind.

195
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,470
I lied that the three of us
gained the foresight,

196
00:09:33,470 --> 00:09:34,730
and fooled him for now.

197
00:09:35,470 --> 00:09:37,900
But just in case Xie Yong'er's story
doesn't match ours,

198
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:39,340
we need to stage a supernatural event

199
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:40,300
to scare her.

200
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,630
Anyway, we can't let Prince Duan
trick her into talking.

201
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:45,320
CEO Dan, I'll leave it to you.

202
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,900
As expected of Wanyin.

203
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:52,390
Noble Consort Yu's handwriting...

204
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:54,070
Dan, you can actually read it?

205
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:57,000
Mr. Bei.

206
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,360
I might have to trouble you

207
00:09:59,590 --> 00:10:00,990
in the time that follows.

208
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:08,830
Crown Prince.

209
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:13,420
[15 years ago]

210
00:10:10,150 --> 00:10:10,660
Dot.

211
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:12,360
Horizontal.

212
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:13,230
Vertical.

213
00:10:13,590 --> 00:10:13,940
Rise.

214
00:10:14,940 --> 00:10:18,490
[Young Xiahou Dan]

215
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:15,910
Left-falling.

216
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:17,560
Right-falling.

217
00:10:19,590 --> 00:10:21,720
Master writing the character "Yong,"

218
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:22,750
and you can write

219
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,190
all other characters well.

220
00:10:24,190 --> 00:10:24,920
Practice it.

221
00:10:26,050 --> 00:10:29,340
[Yong]

222
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:39,230
Isn't this book called

223
00:10:39,230 --> 00:10:41,870
"Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort."

224
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,590
There's gotta be a transmigrated heroine

225
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:45,540
with a protagonist plot, right?

226
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:48,270
Where on earth is she?

227
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:55,130
[Yong]

228
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:06,090
[Yong]

229
00:11:09,430 --> 00:11:10,070
Eunuch An.

230
00:11:10,890 --> 00:11:11,980
It is so late.

231
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:14,530
Why did His Majesty suddenly summon me

232
00:11:14,530 --> 00:11:16,200
with so many Imperial Guards?

233
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:17,630
Is something wrong?

234
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:19,540
Your Highness,

235
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:21,770
I am not sure about that.

236
00:11:22,110 --> 00:11:24,040
But ever since you attended to him,

237
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:26,630
His Majesty has been lost in thought alone

238
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:28,370
and always

239
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:30,270
muttering something...

240
00:11:30,770 --> 00:11:32,510
"Those not on my side,

241
00:11:32,950 --> 00:11:34,100
they must..."

242
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:36,670
"They must..."

243
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,910
They must be disloyal?

244
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,710
Yes, that is it.

245
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:42,300
"They must be disloyal."

246
00:11:42,470 --> 00:11:44,330
There is another line after that.

247
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:47,640
What is it?

248
00:11:49,370 --> 00:11:50,810
"Execute them!"

249
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:56,900
Let's go, Your Highness.

250
00:12:18,910 --> 00:12:19,770
Your Highness,

251
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,130
go inside quickly.

252
00:12:21,130 --> 00:12:22,860
His Majesty is waiting for you.

253
00:13:11,420 --> 00:13:13,320
Those not on my side,

254
00:13:14,180 --> 00:13:16,300
they must be disloyal.

255
00:13:17,060 --> 00:13:18,680
Execute them!

256
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:29,700
My dear,

257
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:32,810
I have been waiting for you
for a long time.

258
00:13:34,030 --> 00:13:34,830
Your Majesty,

259
00:13:35,570 --> 00:13:37,470
what's going on here?

260
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:39,970
What is a platform?

261
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,610
What is an idol?

262
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,450
What is the plot?

263
00:13:44,470 --> 00:13:45,730
What is a 2D character?

264
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,160
Your Majesty,

265
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,800
I don't know what you are talking about.

266
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:01,980
The things you told me when you were drunk

267
00:14:02,310 --> 00:14:03,710
were truly interesting.

268
00:14:08,700 --> 00:14:10,040
Who exactly are you?

269
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:12,030
Why do you always know things

270
00:14:12,030 --> 00:14:13,510
that are unheard of?

271
00:14:17,110 --> 00:14:18,020
I am...

272
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:19,820
I...

273
00:14:20,180 --> 00:14:21,310
Perhaps Consort Xie

274
00:14:21,410 --> 00:14:23,000
has gained the foresight

275
00:14:23,610 --> 00:14:25,380
and can foresee the future.

276
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:26,170
Foresight?

277
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:27,360
That's right.

278
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:29,090
Those with roots of wisdom

279
00:14:29,090 --> 00:14:31,490
can predict the future using

280
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,950
drunkenness or dreams.

281
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:36,270
Is that so?

282
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:43,320
Your Majesty,

283
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:45,780
I...

284
00:14:45,940 --> 00:14:47,410
I-I do...

285
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,790
I do know a little about divination.

286
00:14:56,650 --> 00:14:58,310
Why didn't you say so earlier?

287
00:15:00,420 --> 00:15:00,780
Come.

288
00:15:00,970 --> 00:15:01,770
Rise, my dear.

289
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:11,050
These past few days,

290
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:14,250
your drunken ramblings

291
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,780
really scared me to death.

292
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:20,520
So it was all a misunderstanding.

293
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,850
Do not blame me, my dear.

294
00:15:25,410 --> 00:15:26,190
After all,

295
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:31,400
No one wants their bedfellow

296
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,930
to be on the other side.

297
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:09,370
Your Highness?

298
00:16:10,180 --> 00:16:10,800
Yong'er.

299
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:20,080
It's so late in the night—

300
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,580
why are you here alone?

301
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:26,690
Your Highness,

302
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:29,590
His Majesty is busy
with official business,

303
00:16:29,590 --> 00:16:30,940
s-so I...

304
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,420
did not stay the night,

305
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,450
and wanted to take a walk.

306
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:37,720
Why are you here?

307
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:39,390
His Majesty summoned me

308
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:41,070
to discuss matters.

309
00:16:43,990 --> 00:16:45,120
What a coincidence.

310
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:55,880
Ever since the library fire,

311
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:59,230
it has been inconvenient for me
to come to the harem.

312
00:16:59,230 --> 00:17:00,380
Seeing you

313
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:04,079
is harder than ascending to the heavens.

314
00:17:04,950 --> 00:17:05,760
Yes.

315
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:09,230
We haven't seen each other
for a long time.

316
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:11,849
Then why did you

317
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,250
not write to me?

318
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:17,500
His Majesty and the Empress Dowager

319
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:18,900
have people watching me.

320
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:21,680
No matter how selfish I am,

321
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:27,339
how could I put my beloved

322
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:29,070
in danger?

323
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:34,440
Your Highness...

324
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:37,470
I have one more question.

325
00:17:38,260 --> 00:17:39,500
The silk pouch you gave me,

326
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:41,100
contained a brilliant plan.

327
00:17:41,220 --> 00:17:42,550
It was truly ingenious.

328
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:45,300
But you stay in the harem all day,

329
00:17:46,170 --> 00:17:48,300
and have no contact with those people.

330
00:17:49,150 --> 00:17:50,560
How did you know

331
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:53,090
about these secrets?

332
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,850
I...

333
00:17:56,870 --> 00:17:59,110
no one wants their bedfellow

334
00:18:02,180 --> 00:18:03,590
to be on the other side.

335
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:05,260
What is it?

336
00:18:07,790 --> 00:18:08,500
I

337
00:18:09,900 --> 00:18:11,360
know a little divination.

338
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,970
I often see things about the future

339
00:18:13,970 --> 00:18:15,350
in my dreams.

340
00:18:16,590 --> 00:18:17,920
Something like that...

341
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:20,840
Your Highness,

342
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:23,210
you can understand it this way.

343
00:18:23,930 --> 00:18:25,390
I'm the kind of person
described in storybooks

344
00:18:25,390 --> 00:18:26,590
who knows divination

345
00:18:26,690 --> 00:18:29,130
and gains foresight through dreams.

346
00:18:30,110 --> 00:18:32,510
Otherwise, how could I foresee the future?

347
00:18:38,130 --> 00:18:39,940
It's just that when these dreams come

348
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:41,150
and whether they are accurate

349
00:18:41,150 --> 00:18:42,080
depend entirely

350
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:44,350
on heaven's will.

351
00:18:44,740 --> 00:18:45,740
That is why I never

352
00:18:45,740 --> 00:18:47,200
told you the truth before.

353
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:49,150
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

354
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:51,370
Your Highness,

355
00:18:51,370 --> 00:18:52,430
someone is coming.

356
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:02,760
Don't worry.

357
00:19:04,420 --> 00:19:05,960
I will keep your secret.

358
00:19:19,790 --> 00:19:21,200
Did Xie Yong'er really say that

359
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:21,860
last night?

360
00:19:22,980 --> 00:19:23,790
Word for word.

361
00:19:26,150 --> 00:19:27,210
Thank you, Mr. Bei,

362
00:19:27,260 --> 00:19:28,720
for eavesdropping for me.

363
00:19:29,830 --> 00:19:31,620
Anything for you.

364
00:19:33,490 --> 00:19:34,160
How is she?

365
00:19:34,820 --> 00:19:36,670
She was scared out of her wits.

366
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:38,790
I mean Wanyin.

367
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:39,980
Her?

368
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:42,480
She laughed so hard.

369
00:19:43,540 --> 00:19:46,330
You actually summoned Prince Duan
to the palace on purpose

370
00:19:46,330 --> 00:19:48,260
to create opportunities for them.

371
00:19:49,190 --> 00:19:49,980
CEO Dan!

372
00:19:50,450 --> 00:19:51,880
You're terrible!

373
00:19:52,390 --> 00:19:53,970
I've settled the scholars.

374
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:56,170
When can we get rid of Xie Yong'er?

375
00:19:56,700 --> 00:19:58,260
I make her drunk every day.

376
00:19:58,700 --> 00:19:59,960
I can't drink anymore.

377
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,270
Wine is food essence.

378
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:05,550
The more you drink, the younger you get.

379
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:07,700
You have a beauty in your arms,
yet you're unhappy?

380
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:08,430
Keep acting.

381
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:13,130
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

382
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:14,630
It's just two ellipsis—
need I run all the way there?

383
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:14,830
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

384
00:20:15,150 --> 00:20:15,590
Then,

385
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:16,460
♪ Incredible ♪

386
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:17,670
I can add a few more ellipsis?

387
00:20:16,950 --> 00:20:17,980
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

388
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:19,460
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

389
00:20:18,630 --> 00:20:19,930
Don't rush.

390
00:20:19,620 --> 00:20:21,280
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

391
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:22,130
Xie Yong'er
hasn't done anything wrong yet.

392
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:22,760
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

393
00:20:22,390 --> 00:20:23,840
You can't just turn on her, can you?

394
00:20:23,190 --> 00:20:24,510
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

395
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:24,840
Besides,

396
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:27,710
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

397
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:27,950
Prince Duan is wavering back and forth
between Xie Yong'er and me.

398
00:20:27,950 --> 00:20:29,540
♪ From day to night ♪

399
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:29,900
We can't just push Xie Yong'er

400
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,110
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

401
00:20:29,980 --> 00:20:31,180
towards Prince Duan.

402
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,750
♪ From the present to the past ♪

403
00:20:32,870 --> 00:20:34,000
♪ It's always you ♪

404
00:20:34,490 --> 00:20:35,990
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

405
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:36,590
If Xie Yong'er falls out with Prince Duan,

406
00:20:36,010 --> 00:20:37,550
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

407
00:20:36,730 --> 00:20:37,830
do I have to be responsible for her?

408
00:20:37,620 --> 00:20:40,500
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

409
00:20:38,950 --> 00:20:40,580
She is the female lead.

410
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:41,920
She will have plenty of help.

411
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:43,930
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

412
00:20:42,460 --> 00:20:44,090
You should worry about yourself first.

413
00:20:43,980 --> 00:20:45,880
♪ With you ♪

414
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:48,760
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

415
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:47,310
Wait, Mr. Bei.

416
00:20:48,350 --> 00:20:49,430
I missed an exclamation mark.

417
00:20:48,820 --> 00:20:50,400
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

418
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:52,400
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

419
00:20:52,890 --> 00:20:55,180
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

420
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:54,240
What did she say?

421
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:56,740
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

422
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:58,780
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

423
00:20:59,650 --> 00:21:01,250
Are you telling me what to do?

424
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,600
That is right.

425
00:21:05,990 --> 00:21:08,280
Haven't I always been
telling you what to do?

426
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:08,770
Mr. Bei.

427
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:10,750
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

428
00:21:09,610 --> 00:21:10,070
[That is right.]

429
00:21:10,090 --> 00:21:10,530
[Haven't I always been
telling you what to do?]

430
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:12,690
How long are you two
going to talk like this?

431
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:12,500
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

432
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:13,780
I am just

433
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:16,050
helping Wanyin practice writing.

434
00:21:16,050 --> 00:21:16,660
Look.

435
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:19,080
[That is right.]

436
00:21:18,140 --> 00:21:19,110
Hasn't her handwriting

437
00:21:19,110 --> 00:21:20,630
[Haven't I always been
telling you what to do?]

438
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:20,800
improved?

439
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,610
Come hit me if you dare.

440
00:21:25,690 --> 00:21:26,910
♪ Incredible ♪

441
00:21:27,290 --> 00:21:28,470
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

442
00:21:28,890 --> 00:21:29,920
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

443
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:30,970
You aren't practicing calligraphy at all.

444
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:31,780
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

445
00:21:31,700 --> 00:21:32,490
I think

446
00:21:32,110 --> 00:21:33,130
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

447
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:34,630
you are just wasting my internal force.

448
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:34,890
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

449
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:38,100
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

450
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:38,440
Thank you for your trouble, Mr. Bei.

451
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:40,020
♪ From day to night ♪

452
00:21:39,140 --> 00:21:39,740
By the way,

453
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:41,630
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

454
00:21:40,290 --> 00:21:41,690
two scholars are coming later.

455
00:21:41,690 --> 00:21:43,240
♪ From the present to the past ♪

456
00:21:42,220 --> 00:21:43,030
Wanyin

457
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:44,820
might need to work remotely with everyone.

458
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:44,420
♪ It's always you ♪

459
00:21:44,970 --> 00:21:46,400
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

460
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:46,390
No, I mean—

461
00:21:46,470 --> 00:21:47,980
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

462
00:21:46,930 --> 00:21:48,900
she might need to communicate
via handwritten notes.

463
00:21:48,090 --> 00:21:50,940
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

464
00:21:49,850 --> 00:21:50,690
So...

465
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:52,320
I have to trouble you, Mr. Bei,

466
00:21:51,330 --> 00:21:54,290
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

467
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:54,080
to run a few more errands.

468
00:21:54,350 --> 00:21:56,300
♪ With you ♪

469
00:21:55,550 --> 00:21:55,900
Here.

470
00:21:56,150 --> 00:21:57,650
Talk face to face.

471
00:21:56,850 --> 00:21:59,210
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

472
00:21:58,550 --> 00:21:59,190
Talk.

473
00:21:59,330 --> 00:22:00,830
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

474
00:22:00,900 --> 00:22:02,800
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

475
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:03,340
Your Majesty, why did you summon me?

476
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:05,600
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

477
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:05,320
It's not appropriate for us

478
00:22:05,630 --> 00:22:07,110
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

479
00:22:05,980 --> 00:22:07,200
to meet right now, is it?

480
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,210
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

481
00:22:08,630 --> 00:22:10,350
It's because Li Yunxi and Cen Jintian

482
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:11,550
are coming over soon.

483
00:22:12,390 --> 00:22:15,650
How great is this?
You should've talked like this long ago.

484
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:21,120
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

485
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,900
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

486
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:22,810
Actually,

487
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:26,210
Li Yunxi and Cen Jintian
are coming over in a bit.

488
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:27,720
You can meet them.

489
00:22:28,460 --> 00:22:29,990
I forged identities for them,

490
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:31,450
and gave them a sum of money

491
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:33,110
for them to buy official titles.

492
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:34,300
They've managed to get

493
00:22:34,300 --> 00:22:36,050
minor positions in various ministries.

494
00:22:36,050 --> 00:22:37,250
In the past,

495
00:22:37,530 --> 00:22:39,800
if scholars heard
about getting office this way,

496
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:41,380
they would have turned up their noses

497
00:22:41,380 --> 00:22:42,510
and spat in disgust.

498
00:22:43,180 --> 00:22:45,290
But after the incident at the lake...

499
00:22:46,100 --> 00:22:47,760
It seems they've all grown up.

500
00:23:01,790 --> 00:23:03,250
Greetings, Your Majesty.

501
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:04,010
At ease.

502
00:23:04,070 --> 00:23:05,470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

503
00:23:12,420 --> 00:23:13,700
How inappropriate!

504
00:23:15,310 --> 00:23:17,510
I humbly request Her Highness to leave.

505
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:19,960
Leave?

506
00:23:21,870 --> 00:23:22,740
On the boat that day,

507
00:23:22,740 --> 00:23:24,900
Her Highness's presence
was already overstepping.

508
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:26,940
Today you've even entered
the Imperial Study.

509
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:28,310
The harem interfering in politics

510
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:29,270
is absolutely inappropriate.

511
00:23:29,270 --> 00:23:29,830
Enough!

512
00:23:30,390 --> 00:23:31,190
Your Majesty,

513
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:35,250
I am willing

514
00:23:35,420 --> 00:23:37,600
to advise you even at the cost of my life.

515
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:39,990
They haven't grown up at all.

516
00:23:42,870 --> 00:23:43,830
What should we do?

517
00:23:43,830 --> 00:23:44,390
Watch me.

518
00:23:55,740 --> 00:23:58,270
Mr. Li,
after falling into the water that day,

519
00:23:58,630 --> 00:23:59,890
how are your injuries?

520
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:01,310
Are you

521
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:03,230
fully recovered now?

522
00:24:06,830 --> 00:24:07,180
Come!

523
00:24:07,560 --> 00:24:08,560
Give me your hand!

524
00:24:10,550 --> 00:24:11,480
I've recovered.

525
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:14,820
Mr. Li, please calm down first.

526
00:24:15,590 --> 00:24:17,450
It's not too late to advise later.

527
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:23,490
This hand of mine

528
00:24:25,010 --> 00:24:26,340
is practically ruined.

529
00:24:36,220 --> 00:24:38,150
That's Best Actress level acting.

530
00:24:44,830 --> 00:24:45,350
Mr. Li,

531
00:24:46,410 --> 00:24:47,670
have a cup of tea first.

532
00:24:50,650 --> 00:24:51,480
I will...

533
00:24:52,740 --> 00:24:53,890
take my leave now.

534
00:24:54,630 --> 00:24:55,170
Wanyin!

535
00:25:04,570 --> 00:25:06,570
You work tirelessly
for the country

536
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:08,110
and the people.

537
00:25:09,850 --> 00:25:11,550
I see them all.

538
00:25:13,600 --> 00:25:14,460
But some people

539
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:18,800
are so full of prejudice
that they can't tolerate you.

540
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:23,190
Even I feel ashamed for them.

541
00:25:23,550 --> 00:25:25,030
I am just a woman after all.

542
00:25:27,360 --> 00:25:28,580
In this country,

543
00:25:30,510 --> 00:25:32,220
there may be no place for me.

544
00:25:33,700 --> 00:25:35,630
Great righteousness and kindness

545
00:25:36,890 --> 00:25:38,390
have nothing to do with me.

546
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:39,840
Your Highness,

547
00:25:39,980 --> 00:25:40,390
I...

548
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:42,630
If it weren't for Your Highness that day,

549
00:25:42,630 --> 00:25:44,090
we wouldn't be here today.

550
00:25:48,500 --> 00:25:49,460
Your Highness is noble.

551
00:25:49,460 --> 00:25:51,780
I am willing to atone with my death.

552
00:25:55,900 --> 00:25:56,550
Done.

553
00:25:56,790 --> 00:25:57,660
Easy.

554
00:25:59,550 --> 00:26:00,750
He even knelt for you.

555
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:02,850
Piece of cake.

556
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:12,790
Lord Jia.

557
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:15,520
Your Highness.

558
00:26:15,550 --> 00:26:17,590
General Luo had someone send back a horse

559
00:26:17,590 --> 00:26:18,560
and a letter.

560
00:26:24,890 --> 00:26:28,620
[For Prince Duan to receive personally]

561
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:36,110
In this life,

562
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:37,630
I have few fortunes.

563
00:26:38,220 --> 00:26:39,590
Fighting on the battlefield

564
00:26:39,590 --> 00:26:41,310
to serve the country is one.

565
00:26:42,130 --> 00:26:43,400
Meeting His Highness

566
00:26:43,700 --> 00:26:46,560
and fighting the Yan rebels together
is the second.

567
00:26:46,870 --> 00:26:49,070
Whenever I recall
our three years of bitter war—

568
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:50,590
how there was no distinction
between ruler and subject,

569
00:26:50,590 --> 00:26:52,100
only the bond of comrades—

570
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:54,100
I find it even more precious.

571
00:26:54,980 --> 00:26:57,290
I return His Highness's warhorse

572
00:26:57,420 --> 00:26:58,880
as a token of my sincerity.

573
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:01,400
I, Luo Changsheng, kneel in thanks.

574
00:27:08,670 --> 00:27:11,630
General Luo
is truly a man of deep loyalty.

575
00:27:13,340 --> 00:27:14,850
He is reminding me

576
00:27:16,150 --> 00:27:17,750
not to forget to save his son.

577
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,640
First, the Minister of Revenue,

578
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:23,280
and now, Grand Tutor Wei.

579
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:24,900
The Empress Dowager

580
00:27:24,900 --> 00:27:27,150
blames us for all this.

581
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:29,580
She won't let it go easily.

582
00:27:29,890 --> 00:27:31,710
But by forcing my hand like this,

583
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:34,540
even with our deep bonds and history,

584
00:27:35,040 --> 00:27:36,370
it is difficult to do it.

585
00:27:37,600 --> 00:27:38,190
But...

586
00:27:38,800 --> 00:27:40,380
if we do nothing,

587
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:42,800
General Luo might turn against us.

588
00:27:43,530 --> 00:27:45,840
The Empress Dowager has Luo Yi too.

589
00:27:46,010 --> 00:27:47,870
That puts us at a disadvantage.

590
00:27:48,180 --> 00:27:49,180
Usually,

591
00:27:49,290 --> 00:27:52,550
the Empress Dowager uses Luo Yi
to keep General Luo in line.

592
00:27:52,570 --> 00:27:54,120
But in a crisis,

593
00:27:54,660 --> 00:27:57,330
he could become a weapon used against us.

594
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:00,270
So we have to do this.

595
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:04,360
Send a message to Mr. Murong.

596
00:28:04,730 --> 00:28:06,190
Ask him if he has any ideas.

597
00:28:06,980 --> 00:28:07,700
That way,

598
00:28:08,700 --> 00:28:10,700
we can distract the Empress Dowager

599
00:28:11,410 --> 00:28:13,120
so she won't trouble Luo Yi.

600
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:16,030
It will also show General Luo

601
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:17,750
that we are doing our part.

602
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:18,570
Yes.

603
00:28:26,350 --> 00:28:27,210
Your Highness.

604
00:28:27,520 --> 00:28:28,380
Your Highness.

605
00:28:28,430 --> 00:28:29,170
T-Then...

606
00:28:29,820 --> 00:28:31,080
What about this horse?

607
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:33,580
You can have it.

608
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:36,210
Thank you, Your Highness.

609
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:40,700
Military officials
returning to the capital to report

610
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:42,560
must not stay longer than 15 days.

611
00:28:42,700 --> 00:28:45,740
General Luo didn't leave
until the morning of the 16th day.

612
00:28:45,740 --> 00:28:47,700
This can be either a minor or major issue.

613
00:28:46,970 --> 00:28:50,520
[Chen Danian,
Chen Dasui's brother]

614
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:50,080
I can find an excuse

615
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:52,370
to charge him with perverting the law.

616
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:56,940
Don't we have his son?

617
00:28:57,150 --> 00:28:59,250
Instead of convicting him,

618
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:03,230
why not find a way
to make him useful to us?

619
00:29:04,980 --> 00:29:06,300
Lord Chen,

620
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:09,750
don't just talk.

621
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:11,700
Don't be like your brother.

622
00:29:11,730 --> 00:29:13,220
Use your brain.

623
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:14,330
Yes.

624
00:29:16,550 --> 00:29:17,550
Empress Dowager,

625
00:29:17,710 --> 00:29:20,240
I have finished confiscating
the Wei estate.

626
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:21,380
We seized

627
00:29:21,630 --> 00:29:24,110
15 property deeds
and 20,000 taels of gold.

628
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:27,760
Here is the inventory.

629
00:29:30,970 --> 00:29:33,730
Grand Tutor Wei
was convicted by the Emperor.

630
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:35,400
Let him handle it.

631
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:38,710
His Majesty is unfamiliar
with state affairs.

632
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:41,500
Matters of the court, big or small,

633
00:29:41,690 --> 00:29:44,260
still require your decision,
Your Majesty.

634
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:51,710
Which should go to the treasury,

635
00:29:51,940 --> 00:29:53,630
and which should not—

636
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,760
it is your decision, Your Majesty.

637
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:11,510
[Great Xia Agriculture]

638
00:30:11,590 --> 00:30:15,510
[Sweet Potato]

639
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:18,660
[Great Xia Agriculture]

640
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:27,750
How long have you been

641
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:29,640
recording in this book?

642
00:30:30,830 --> 00:30:32,070
About 10 years.

643
00:30:33,360 --> 00:30:34,350
For these 10 years,

644
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:35,830
I have maintained across Great Xia

645
00:30:35,830 --> 00:30:38,070
a small experimental field in each region.

646
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:40,440
It was to study the climate, soil,

647
00:30:40,630 --> 00:30:43,460
planting times, irrigation methods,
and other factors' impact

648
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:44,610
on the harvest.

649
00:30:45,420 --> 00:30:46,790
I now have a system on

650
00:30:46,830 --> 00:30:48,730
what to plant and how to plant

651
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:50,220
in which area.

652
00:30:51,010 --> 00:30:51,540
Lord Cen,

653
00:30:52,450 --> 00:30:53,700
do the crops listed

654
00:30:54,120 --> 00:30:55,350
include Yan millet?

655
00:30:55,870 --> 00:30:56,590
Yan millet?

656
00:30:58,110 --> 00:30:59,120
It should be...

657
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:01,340
just some sporadic records.

658
00:31:01,870 --> 00:31:04,110
It is not common in Great Xia.

659
00:31:04,470 --> 00:31:06,500
What about other drought-resistant crops?

660
00:31:06,500 --> 00:31:08,190
Why do you ask, Your Highness?

661
00:31:19,390 --> 00:31:21,150
The Imperial Astronomer reports

662
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:22,980
an anomaly in the celestial phenomena.

663
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:24,180
In the next two years,

664
00:31:24,830 --> 00:31:26,560
there will be a severe drought.

665
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:32,820
This matter

666
00:31:33,690 --> 00:31:34,500
is top secret.

667
00:31:38,450 --> 00:31:39,010
I

668
00:31:39,350 --> 00:31:40,630
will not leak a word.

669
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,130
It hasn't happened yet.

670
00:31:45,790 --> 00:31:46,790
If we prepare now,

671
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:48,180
when the time comes,

672
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:49,240
no one will starve.

673
00:31:51,500 --> 00:31:52,300
Official Cen?

674
00:31:54,110 --> 00:31:56,760
Although Yan millet tastes poor,

675
00:31:56,940 --> 00:31:58,700
it ripens two to three times a year.

676
00:31:58,700 --> 00:32:00,270
If planted widely,

677
00:32:01,030 --> 00:32:03,490
it could indeed
save lives during a drought.

678
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:05,710
Great Xia

679
00:32:06,270 --> 00:32:08,530
has no tradition of planting Yan millet.

680
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:10,230
To start planting now,

681
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:12,240
we must first convince the people.

682
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,550
As for Yan millet seeds,

683
00:32:13,550 --> 00:32:14,750
perhaps the court can

684
00:32:14,870 --> 00:32:16,530
purchase them from Yan State.

685
00:32:17,900 --> 00:32:19,160
The treasury is empty.

686
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:21,850
The court has no money.

687
00:32:30,980 --> 00:32:33,900
And there is much friction on the border
between Yan State and Great Xia.

688
00:32:33,900 --> 00:32:34,700
And now,

689
00:32:35,390 --> 00:32:37,830
the military power
is entirely in Prince Duan's hands,

690
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:39,830
and the national treasury is empty.

691
00:32:40,620 --> 00:32:42,280
Neither soft nor hard tactics

692
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:43,610
can be implemented.

693
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:47,270
But I must introduce Yan millet

694
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:49,800
to save the people from disaster.

695
00:32:50,750 --> 00:32:51,350
That is why

696
00:32:52,740 --> 00:32:54,270
I have gathered you all here

697
00:32:54,390 --> 00:32:55,650
to discuss a solution.

698
00:32:57,150 --> 00:32:58,110
I have an idea.

699
00:32:58,790 --> 00:33:00,720
We might not need to spend any money

700
00:33:00,830 --> 00:33:01,690
to obtain

701
00:33:02,110 --> 00:33:04,040
a large amount of Yan millet seeds.

702
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:07,080
Can you be more specific?

703
00:33:11,070 --> 00:33:12,400
We shall take our leave.

704
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:29,780
What's wrong?

705
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,050
Is your head hurting again?

706
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:38,410
A little.

707
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:50,250
These ministers

708
00:33:50,630 --> 00:33:52,290
are actually quite reliable.

709
00:33:53,850 --> 00:33:55,180
Let's follow their plan

710
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,240
step by step.

711
00:33:56,730 --> 00:33:57,790
Maybe we really can

712
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,380
prevent the drought.

713
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:00,900
Yes.

714
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,330
You finally have

715
00:34:03,630 --> 00:34:05,290
right-hand men,

716
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:07,500
no longer fighting alone.

717
00:34:08,199 --> 00:34:10,130
But you don't sound happy about it.

718
00:34:14,739 --> 00:34:17,670
Are we being too optimistic?

719
00:34:19,730 --> 00:34:20,790
What if Prince Duan

720
00:34:21,530 --> 00:34:23,659
and the Empress Dowager get in our way?

721
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:25,210
Or what if

722
00:34:26,460 --> 00:34:27,639
they get suspicious

723
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:29,699
and discover our entire plan?

724
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:31,860
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

725
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:32,659
Leave it to me.

726
00:34:40,489 --> 00:34:42,620
So you've already thought it through.

727
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:48,070
Wanyin.

728
00:34:49,110 --> 00:34:49,639
Sit down.

729
00:35:02,780 --> 00:35:03,840
There's something

730
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:06,910
I've been wanting
to ask you for a long time.

731
00:35:07,970 --> 00:35:09,700
Who do you think leaked the news

732
00:35:09,730 --> 00:35:12,280
of our meeting
with the scholars on the lake

733
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:15,300
to Prince Duan?

734
00:35:19,330 --> 00:35:21,260
I haven't figured that out either.

735
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:22,800
You think it was me,

736
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:24,680
right?

737
00:35:27,040 --> 00:35:29,300
You think I leaked the news
to Prince Duan,

738
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:31,300
then put on a show for the scholars,

739
00:35:32,340 --> 00:35:33,480
going so far as to

740
00:35:33,860 --> 00:35:35,160
sacrifice a life

741
00:35:35,910 --> 00:35:37,570
just to win their trust.

742
00:35:41,810 --> 00:35:42,420
Oh, right.

743
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:44,400
The fire in the library—

744
00:35:44,860 --> 00:35:46,410
do you also think I did it?

745
00:35:47,150 --> 00:35:48,820
After all, judging by the outcome,

746
00:35:48,820 --> 00:35:50,480
Xu Yao was backed into a corner

747
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:52,890
and indeed handed over that book.

748
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:55,740
And all these incidents,

749
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:58,250
the one who benefited the most

750
00:35:58,470 --> 00:35:58,990
was me.

751
00:36:00,940 --> 00:36:02,340
It's not because of that.

752
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:10,000
Then why?

753
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:15,870
That day on the boat,

754
00:36:16,520 --> 00:36:19,120
we talked to the scholars
for four whole hours.

755
00:36:20,220 --> 00:36:21,730
Today in the Imperial Study,

756
00:36:21,730 --> 00:36:23,590
we talked for another four hours.

757
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:25,500
You said a lot

758
00:36:25,890 --> 00:36:27,750
and showed off a lot of knowledge,

759
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:29,690
but your knowledge of economics

760
00:36:29,690 --> 00:36:31,250
is just as sad as mine.

761
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:38,170
Which company are you from?

762
00:36:39,350 --> 00:36:40,970
What does this company do?

763
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,190
When was it listed?

764
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,630
What was its market value

765
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:47,770
before you came here?

766
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:52,000
Who are you?
